The band consists of Conor Mason (lead vocals and guitar), Joe Langridge-Brown (guitar), Dominic Craik (guitar and keyboard), Philip Blake (bass), and James Price (drums) [sonymusic](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/id/0-3) [wikipedia](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/id/0-0). In 2014, they signed with RCA Records and released their self-titled debut album in October 2015 [wikipedia](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/id/0-0). Their fourth studio album, *Dead Club City*, released in June 2023, became their first UK No. 1 album [wikipedia](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/id/0-0).
